title: Course Requirement check for undergraduate Students
content: To check your course requirement for graduation, send an email to CS department office and visit to see the result. ※ To apply for check up: Send email to csdept@cs.kaist.ac.kr [Title]: 2012.02 Graduation -(student id#)(name)" [Content]: name: student id#: registered class for 2011 Fall: cell phone number: date to visit department office (from 2011.09.05 to 2011.09.09 only, at least 1 day after apply) ※ Applying period: 2011.09.02(Fri) ~ 2011.09.08(Thu) ※ For Inquiries: Ms. JiYeon Lee(042-350-3505)
